ht":2160,"file_path":"/bxlY1FFIeAiY2QFiByFRJYEMiqW.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/ojYkFBZOjZZPqbwDShTWvXmcBXx.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/brAI6pyvBsLKgePQh3BjniOE1xd.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T11:49:27.163+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":110,"tagline":"打破成见 做自己的英雄。","homepage":"","overview":"天地灵气孕育出一颗能量巨大的混元珠，元始天尊将混元珠提炼成灵珠和魔丸，灵珠投胎为人，助周伐纣时可堪大用；而魔丸则会诞出魔王，为祸人间。元始天尊启动了天劫咒语，3年后天雷将会降临，摧毁魔丸。太乙受命将灵珠托生于陈塘关李靖家的儿子哪吒身上。然而阴差阳错，灵珠和魔丸竟然被掉包。本应是灵珠英雄的哪吒却成了混世大魔王。调皮捣蛋顽劣不堪的哪吒却徒有一颗做英雄的心。然而面对众人对魔丸的误解和即将来临的天雷的降临，哪吒是否命中注定会立地成魔？他将何去何从？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":110,"tagline":"Fight your fate","homepage":"https://www.wellgousa.com/films/ne-zha","overview":"A young boy is born as the reincarnation of a demonic power, into a society that hates and fears him. Destined by prophecy to bring destruction to the world, Nezha must choose between good and evil to see if he can change his fate."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"哪吒之魔童降世","runtime":110,"tagline":"生而為魔 那又如何","homepage":"","overview":"太乙受命將靈珠托生給李靖家的兒子哪吒身上，卻被掉包，使得哪吒變成混世大魔王。有顆英雄心的他，面對眾人對魔完的誤解和即將在三年後摧毀魔丸的天雷，將何去何從？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"나타지마동강세","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"태을진인의 실수로 영주(선) 대신 마환(악)은 이정의 아들 나타로 환생한다. 3년 후, 천겁을 맞고 사라져야 할 운명을 타고난 나타는 마을을 혼란에 빠트려 사람들의 미움을 사게 된다. 세상에 파멸을 가져올 운명을 짊어진 나타의 마지막은 과연…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Нэчжа","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Небо и земля породили Жемчужину Хаоса, обладающую огромной силой, и образовавшийся демон сразу начал бушевать. Небесный владыка усмирил существо, разделил жемчужину на две — Жемчужину Духа и Жемчужину Демона — и заточил обе в цветок лотоса. А также наказал бессмертному Тайи проследить, чтобы Жемчужина Духа переродилась в третьего сына правителя Ли Цзына, которого следует назвать Нэчжа, а на Жемчужину Демона наложил судьбу — через три года она будет разрушена ударом молнии. Но другой бессмертный по имени Ян Вэй перед самым рождением наследника крадет Жемчужину Духа, и демон вселяется в младенца. Только появившись на свет, Нэчжа начинает кидаться в население файерболами, сея хаос, ужас и разрушения, поэтому Тайи надевает на него золотой усмиряющий ошейник. Правитель Ли Цзин просит оставить малыша в живых и клянётся, что не позволит ему покидать дворец, ведь всё равно через три года Нэчжу настигнет смертельное проклятие."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":0,"tagline":"Lucha contra tu destino","homepage":"","overview":"Nezha, nacido de una perla celestial con poderes únicos, pronto se encontrará exiliado, odiado y temido por la gente que cree en una profecía que indica que él traerá la destrucción del mundo. Llegará el momento en el que deberá decidir entre el bien y el mal con el propósito de romper los grilletes del destino y convertirse en un héroe. Película inspirada muy libremente en \"Fengshen Yanyi\" (\"La Investidura de los Dioses\"), una de las grandes novelas chinas escritas en la Dinastía Ming cuya autoría se atribuye a Xu Zhonglin o Lu Xixing."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"นาจา","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เมื่อพลังแห่งสวรรค์ และโลกได้ให้กำเนิดไข่มุกพลังวัตรที่หลอมรวมพลังมหาศาลไว้ด้วยกัน \"หยวนสือเทียนจุน\" เทพผู้เป็นใหญ่ที่สุดในสวรรค์จึงสกัดไข่มุกนั้นออกเป็นสองลูก ลูกหนึ่งกลายเป็นไข่มุกสวรรค์ ส่วนอีกลูกเป็นโอสถปีศาจ ก่อนจะนำพวกมันไปเก็บไว้ในบัววิเศษเจ็ดสี ไข่มุกสวรรค์ถูกกำหนดให้จุติเป็นมนุษย์ที่จะมีส่วนในการก่อตั้งราชวงศ์โจว ในขณะที่โอสถปีศาจถูกลิขิตให้จุติเป็นปีศาจร้ายที่จะมาทำลายล้างโลก เพื่อป้องกันไม่ให้เหตุการณ์นี้เกิดขึ้น หยวนสือเทียนจุน จึงได้ร่ายคาถาฟ้าพิโรธใส่โอสถปีศาจเพื่อให้มันถูกทำลายภายในเวลาสามปี \"เทพไท่อี่\" ได้รับบัญชาให้นำไข่มุกสวรรค์ไปจุติในครอบครัวของ \"แม่ทัพหลี่จิ้ง\" เพื่อให้กำเนิดบุตรขึ้นมาและตั้งชื่อว่า \"นาจา\" แต่เหตุการณ์กลับไม่เป็นเช่นนั้น เมื่อพญามังกรได้สลับไข่มุกสวรรค์กับโอสถปีศาจ นาจา จึงถือกำเนิดขึ้นมาด้วยพลังโอสถปีศาจ จากลิขิตสวรรค์ที่จะต้องเกิดมาเพื่อช่วยเหลือมนุษย์ กลับกลายเป็นพญามารผู้ที่จะมาก่อภัยพิบัติขึ้นซะเอง นาจาจะฝ่าฟันต่อชะตากรรมที่ถูกกำหนดไว้อย่างไร และจะพบจุดจบแบบไหน ศึกแห่งชะตากรรมครั้งนี้ได้ระเบิดขึ้นแล้ว!!!"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Nezha: A Démongyermek születése","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Különleges képességei birtokában, Nezha-nak démonokkal kell megküzdenie, hogy megvédhesse azokat az embereket, akik rettegnek tőle.​\"Ha a sorsod kegyetlen, csak küzdj ellene a végsőkig."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":110,"tagline":"Eu sou o destino","homepage":"","overview":"O Primus extrai uma pérola mista de Yuan que contém uma Semente Espiritual e uma Pílula Demoníaca. A Semente Espiritual pode ser reencarnada como um humano para ajudar o Rei Zhou a estabelecer uma nova dinastia, enquanto a Pílula Demoníaca criará um demônio ameaçando a humanidade. Ne Zha é quem está destinado a ser o herói, mas ele se torna um demónio encarnado, porque a Semente Espiritual e a Pílula Demoníaca são trocadas."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"\"Ne Zha\" conta a história de um jovem prodígio, nascido como um demônio e destinado a trazer destruição, que luta contra o seu destino para se tornar um herói.  Ele nasce da união de uma pérola celestial e um coração de um demônio, amaldiçoado a trazer destruição ao mundo.  Por causa da sua origem demoníaca, Ne Zha é odiado e temido por todos, sendo forçado a lutar contra os seus próprios demônios interiores para provar o seu valor e mudar o seu destino. O filme acompanha a sua jornada enquanto ele tenta quebrar os grilhões do seu destino, escolhendo o bem em vez do mal para se tornar o herói que ele quer ser."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Неза","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Филм заснован на лику из кинеске митологије, који се појављује у неким од најбољих дела кинеске класичне литературе. Незха је дечак-бог, који се нађе на удару својих саплеменика због тога што пророчанство каже да ће донети пропаст свету. Због тога је принуђен да бира између сила добра и зла, али ће успети да се одупре искушењима судбине и постане херој за сва времена."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ne zha, un jeune garçon, est né d'une perle céleste du Seigneur du ciel. Doté de pouvoirs uniques, il se retrouve à vivre comme un paria, détesté et craint. Destiné par la prophétie à détruire le monde, il doit choisir entre le bien et le mal afin de briser les chaînes du destin et devenir un héros."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Nezha","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Perla chaosu, zrozená z prapůvodních esencí, začala lačně pohlcovat energii. Když jeho žáci Taiyi Zhenren a Shen Gongbao v boji s Perlou chaosu selhali, rozdělil ji božský stvořitel Nebe a Země Yuanshi Tianzun na dva protiklady: Duchovní perlu a Démonickou kouli. Protože moc Démonické koule byla příliš velká a riziko zničení lidstva z ní plynoucí příliš vysoké, odsoudil ji bůh Yuanshi Tianzun nezrušitelnou nebeskou kletbou ke zničení mocným bleskem za tři roky. S Duchovní perlou poslal svého žáka Taiyi na Zem, aby se tam reinkarnovala jako třetí syn velícího důstojníka Li Jing-a, dostala jméno Ne Zha a stala se bojovníkem proti démonům."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Na Tra: Ma Đồng Giáng Thế","runtime":109,"tagline":"Là tiên hay ma, tự ta định đoạt.","homepage":"","overview":"Từ thuở xa xưa, tinh hoa đất trời hội tụ thành một viên ngọc chứa đựng năng lượng khổng lồ. Nguyên Thủy Thiên Tôn đã phân tách viên ngọc này thành 1 viên Linh Châu và 1 viên Ma Hoàn. Viên Linh Châu sẽ đầu thai thành một anh hùng cứu thế, phò trợ nhà Chu. Trong khi đó, Ma Hoàn sẽ tạo ra một Ma Vương tàn sát thiên hạ. Để ngăn chặn thảm họa, Nguyên Thủy Thiên Tôn đã hạ chú để sau 3 năm Ma Vương sẽ bị Thiên kiếp tiêu diệt. Liệu Na Tra có đủ sức để thay đổi Thiên mệnh?"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Γεννημένος με μοναδικές δυνάμεις, ένα αγόρι στρατολογείτε για να πολεμήσει  τους δαίμονες και να σώσει την κοινότητα του που τον φοβάται."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Primus, bir Karışık Yuan Boncuğunu bir Ruh Tohumu ve bir İblis Hapına dönüştürür. Ruh Tohumu, Kral Zhou'nun yeni bir hanedan kurmasına yardım etmek için bir insan olarak reenkarne edilebilirken, İblis Hapı insanlığı tehdit eden bir şeytan yaratacaktır. Ne Zha, kaderinde kahraman olan kişidir, ancak bunun yerine enkarne bir şeytan olur, çünkü Ruh Tohumu ve Şeytan Hapı değiştirilir."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"نژا","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"داستان در مورد پسری است که با قدرت‌های فرا انسانی متولد شده و اکنون برای مبارزه با شیاطین و نجات جامعه دست‌به‌کار می‌شود…"},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"哪吒之魔童降世","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"元始天尊將混元珠提煉成靈珠和魔丸兩顆，本應是靈珠轉世的哪吒因為太乙真人的失誤被魔丸託生，生來便注定是混世魔王。父母並沒有因為他是魔丸而拋棄他，在太乙真人的幫助下，希望哪吒可以學習本領，為民除害，但叛逆的他並沒有得到陳塘關人民的認可。期間，哪吒認識了龍王之子敖丙，成為了彼此各自唯一的朋友。面對人們的誤解和天雷的降臨，生而為魔的哪吒卻沒有屈從於命運安排，最後憑藉一己之力挽救了蒼生。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":110,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Il giovane Nezha è nato da una perla celeste del Signore Primordiale dei Cieli. Con poteri unici e straordinari, si è ritrovato presto emarginato, odiato e temuto. Destinato da un’antica profezia a portare distruzione nel mondo, Nezha dovrà scegliere tra il bene e il male per spezzare le catene del destino e diventare un eroe…"},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"ナタ～魔童降臨～","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha: Demonpojken från himlen","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En pojke född med unika krafter rekryteras för att bekämpa demoner och rädda samhället som fruktar honom."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nezha, nacido de una perla celestial con poderes únicos, pronto se encontrará exiliado, odiado y temido por la gente que cree en una profecía que indica que él traerá la destrucción del mundo. Llegará el momento en el que deberá decidir entre el bien y el mal con el propósito de romper los grilletes del destino y convertirse en un héroe. Película inspirada muy libremente en \"Fengshen Yanyi\" (\"La Investidura de los Dioses\"), una de las grandes novelas chinas escritas en la Dinastía Ming cuya autoría se atribuye a Xu Zhonglin o Lu Xixing."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Нечжа: народження демона","runtime":110,"tagline":"Ламай стереотипи і будь своїм героєм. Моя доля залежить від мене.","homepage":"","overview":"Земна стихія створила Перлину Хаосу, наділену величезною силою, яка відразу ж почала нестримно бушувати. Небесний владика не зміг спокійно спостерігати, як цей демон вносить хаос у світ, і приборкав істоту, розколовши перлину на дві частини. Однією з них стала Перлина Духа, а другою — Перлина Демона. Обидві частини перлини він заточив у квітці лотоса і наказав безсмертному Тайі охороняти Перлину Духа, поки вона не переродиться в третього сина правителя Лі Цзина, і ім'я його буде Нечжа..."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":0,"tagline":"Kämpfe gegen dein Schicksal an.","homepage":"","overview":"Der Sohn einer Gottheit widersetzt sich seinem Schicksal. Er möchte nicht das machen, was von ihm erwartet wird. Stattdessen wird er zum heldenhaften Beschützer der Unschuldigen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Młody chłopiec rodzi się jako reinkarnacja demonicznej mocy w społeczeństwie, które go nienawidzi i się go boi. Przeznaczony przez przepowiednię do sprowadzenia zniszczenia na świat, Nezha musi wybrać między dobrem a złem, aby sprawdzić, czy uda mu się odmienić swój los."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"","iso_639_1":"tl","iso_3166_1":"PH","english_name":"Tagalog"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Primus extrage o Mărgea Yuan Mixtă, transformând-o într-o Sămânță Spirituală și o Pastilă Demonică. Sămânța Spirituală poate fi reîncarnată ca om pentru a-l ajuta pe Regele Zhou să întemeieze o nouă dinastie, în timp ce Pastila Demonică va da naștere unui diavol care amenință omenirea. Ne Zha este destinat să fie eroul, însă, din cauza unei încurcături, Sămânța Spirituală și Pastila Demonică sunt schimbate, iar el devine întruparea unui demon."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"ناچا","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"صبي يولد بقدرات خارقة وغير عادية، ويجرى تجنيده من أجل محاربة الشياطين وإنقاذ مجتمعه الذين يخافون من خطر أولئك الشياطين."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Не Жа","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Филмът е базиран на класическия китайски роман \"Инвеститура на боговете\" и разказва историята на Не Жа, божествено дете, родено със свръхестествени сили. Не Жа е този, който е предопределен да бъде герой, но вместо това той се превръща в въплътен дявол, защото Духовното семе и Демонското хапче са разменени."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Maleni dječak, Ne Zha, rođen je iz nebeskog bisera s jedinstvenim moćima zbog čega ga se mnogi boje i mrze ga. Iako je njegova sudbina da donese razdor u svijet, on će morati sam odlučiti hoće li stati na stranu dobra ili zla, time prkositi proročanstvu i postati junak."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Ne Zha","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ne zha, un jeune garçon, est né d'une perle céleste du Seigneur du ciel. Doté de pouvoirs uniques, il se retrouve à vivre comme un paria, détesté et craint. Destiné par la prophétie à détruire le monde, il doit choisir entre le bien et le mal afin de briser les chaînes du destin et devenir un héros."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"ნე ჯა","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":980477,"adult":false,"title":"Ne Zha 2","video":false,"overview":"After a catastrophic event leaves their bodies destroyed, Ne Zha and Ao Bing are granted a fragile second chance at life. As tensions rise between the dragon clans and celestial forces, the two must undergo a series of perilous trials that will test their bond, challenge their identities, and decide the fate of both mortals and immortals.","genre_ids":[16,14,12,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":27.5165,"vote_count":589,"poster_path":"/cb5NyNrqiCNNoDkA8FfxHAtypdG.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-29","vote_average":8.115,"backdrop_path":"/8btfz81bOJ2lC7cujYBTw03wzg3.jpg","original_title":"哪吒之魔童闹海","original_language":"zh"},{"id":635389,"adult":false,"title":"Jiang Ziya","video":false,"overview":"Atop the ruins of war, top commander Jiang Ziya is given the task to banish the Nine-tailed Fox Demon who threatens all mortals' very existence. When he discovers the Nine-tailed Fox's life linked to the soul of an innocent girl, he is faced with a challenging decision: follow the will of heaven or find his own path to righteousness.","genre_ids":[16,28,14,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4784,"vote_count":211,"poster_path":"/eDq4dGgNHxPbT3Y5S6mfymsQ0rQ.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-01","vote_average":7.268,"backdrop_path":"/6Urx7y2CQQvxIlzk5R0BpOKI2NR.jpg","original_title":"姜子牙","original_language":"zh"},{"id":532753,"adult":false,"title":"Dying to Survive","video":false,"overview":"A Chinese leukaemia patient smuggles cheap but untested pharmaceuticals from India to help hundreds of Chinese people suffering from cancer.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2561,"vote_count":207,"poster_path":"/xxtK8DWdIwdxF5X2TJcIRDSEtE6.jpg","release_date":"2018-07-06","vote_average":8.179,"backdrop_path":"/xNPeL9cvTCCAwlAwq7Vdq9HNJd.jpg","original_title":"我不是药神","original_language":"zh"},{"id":663558,"adult":false,"title":"New Gods: Nezha Reborn","video":false,"overview":"While living as an ordinary deliveryman and motor racing fan, Nezha encounters old nemeses and must rediscover his powers to protect his loved ones.","genre_ids":[16,14,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5704,"vote_count":504,"poster_path":"/np4ScPY04HESKBbpexwstKsipKe.jpg","release_date":"2021-02-06","vote_average":8.061,"backdrop_path":"/4PKfa0zltSrp1BJoLl8zfvYXaac.jpg","original_title":"新神榜：哪吒重生","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1185528,"adult":false,"title":"Legends of the Condor Heroes: The Gallants","video":false,"overview":"Under Genghis Khan, the Mongolian army pushes west to destroy the Jin Dynasty, setting its sights on the Song Dynasty next. Amid internal conflicts among martial arts schools, Guo Jing unites the Central Plains' warriors to defend Xiangyang, embodying courage and loyalty in the fight for the nation.","genre_ids":[28,18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.4584,"vote_count":81,"poster_path":"/fUCFEGFlMIFet9ja72JDAeG1he8.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-29","vote_average":6.944,"backdrop_path":"/1DTIRhw4cpLJlHlrPPbKzq6amHc.jpg","original_title":"射雕英雄传：侠之大者","original_language":"zh"},{"id":406000,"adult":false,"title":"The Teacher","video":false,"overview":"The principal of an elementary school calls a special parents meeting after it’s alleged that the seemingly empathetic and kindly-looking teacher Mrs. Drazděchová uses her students to manipulate their parents.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5234,"vote_count":104,"poster_path":"/3d8KLjAoQsvd6Bw4noQwXhqu3m0.jpg","release_date":"2016-07-21","vote_average":6.875,"backdrop_path":"/jMwkHToxIE7ZsCJgopSX0YYG8c6.jpg","original_title":"Učiteľka","original_language":"sk"},{"id":554205,"adult":false,"title":"A Cool Fish","video":false,"overview":"Cop-turned-security guard Ma Xianyong finds himself in a criminal twilight zone when two unrelated events turn his world upside down. The mysterious disappearance of his boss has implications for his financial security. Even more perilous is the abduction of his paralyzed sister who, unknown to Ma, makes a morbid deal with her captors.","genre_ids":[35,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5637,"vote_count":96,"poster_path":"/xhXIJFaCgnnNxmMc2wWz9J11sey.jpg","release_date":"2018-11-15","vote_average":7.016,"backdrop_path":"/iRBJXdXjATsm0Qnq6JYrBSTQ3qq.jpg","original_title":"无名之辈","original_language":"zh"},{"id":576928,"adult":false,"title":"Asuran","video":false,"overview":"A family from the underprivileged class is on the run after the teenaged son kills a rich man from the upper caste. Can the pacifist father be able to save his hot-blooded son?","genre_ids":[28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7823,"vote_count":100,"poster_path":"/Elnp3XrAlMM30dil8rbL7D9XeP.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-02","vote_average":7.64,"backdrop_path":"/oxl1w7sICYDJfaD9PM06HfPUmOi.jpg","original_title":"அசுரன்","original_language":"ta"},{"id":715253,"adult":false,"title":"Phantom","video":false,"overview":"In 1933, when Korea was under Japanese occupation, five people in Gyeongseong are suspected to be \"Phantom\" spies of the anti-Japanese organization.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.247,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/n1rxZ4wovf7BYhLNwCqde8I3I2N.jpg","release_date":"2023-01-18","vote_average":6.875,"backdrop_path":"/wFzI8o0jEMYfNugglP4wjFIr647.jpg","original_title":"유령","original_language":"ko"},{"id":554779,"adult":false,"title":"Swing Kids","video":false,"overview":"Rebellious Ki-soo from North Korea is mesmerized by tap dance in prison camps. Ki-soo joins as a team member of a dance team named 'Swing Kids'. Yet suddenly, their dreams about dancing in prison camps are put in danger.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6491,"vote_count":81,"poster_path":"/uHTGysp05nfUZ3SJJtAVMjzTsTt.jpg","release_date":"2018-12-14","vote_average":8.148,"backdrop_path":"/lcFV956GbjOY1iOpEnXWuxvdrB9.jpg","original_title":"스윙키즈","original_language":"ko"},{"id":839803,"adult":false,"title":"I Am What I Am","video":false,"overview":"By a fortunate coincidence, Gyun is inspired and encouraged by a girl with the same name. Therefore, he decides to form a lion dance troupe with his friends, Kat and Doggie, to break the constraints of reality and fight for themselves for once.","genre_ids":[16,35,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3893,"vote_count":74,"poster_path":"/901NqAyWFcMoY7o1IJzl8QLbxxU.jpg","release_date":"2021-12-11","vote_average":7.236,"backdrop_path":"/9O5XXzZiXuuog4KLHhBefzJ70HO.jpg","original_title":"雄狮少年","original_language":"zh"},{"id":51763,"adult":false,"title":"The Long Walk Home","video":false,"overview":"Two women, black and white, in 1955 Montgomery Alabama, must decide what they are going to do in response to the famous bus boycott led by Martin Luther King.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0801,"vote_count":153,"poster_path":"/7T2oVjLHHIDY6FQH9e04oOgPWQa.jpg","release_date":"1990-12-21","vote_average":7.634,"backdrop_path":"/wgKWecDF29zSa0nfCx589S4Dejy.jpg","original_title":"The Long Walk Home","original_language":"en"},{"id":191463,"adult":false,"title":"The Troubleshooters","video":false,"overview":"For anyone with tricky personal troubles — marital, professional and otherwise — Yu Guan and his buddies have a new business that will provide the solution, from taking the abuse of a man’s nagging wife to showering an obscure writer with awards.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6122,"vote_count":22,"poster_path":"/x7dGWxmBqozw9PHtRdvZy8Q7XDl.jpg","release_date":"1988-01-01","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/NbW38FatbsQxKjQ0s97eR3LjJi.jpg","original_title":"顽主","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1083637,"adult":false,"title":"Kantara - A Legend: Chapter 1","video":false,"overview":"During the Kadamba reign, King Vijayendra, the ruler of the fictional feudatory land of Bangra, meets his final fate while venturing into the mystical forest of Kantara. Witnessing this, his son Rajashekara seals the borders of their realm. Later, Prince Kulashekara reopens them through a brutal massacre. The protagonist, Berme, in search of prosperity, crosses the divide and ignites a conflict of faith, power, and destiny between the Kingdom and Nature.","genre_ids":[28,18,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.7762,"vote_count":58,"poster_path":"/ehQPboTPaIMkMUOoNOh8e7pZ5Rp.jpg","release_date":"2025-10-01","vote_average":7.017,"backdrop_path":"/w57nxiBIODAYHLRs1xmrCY9zEFe.jpg","original_title":"ಕಾಂತಾರ: ಅಧ್ಯಾಯ - ೧","original_language":"kn"},{"id":576069,"adult":false,"title":"Bait","video":false,"overview":"Martin Ward is a cove fisherman, without a boat. His brother Steven has repurposed their father’s vessel as a tourist tripper, driving a wedge between the brothers. With their childhood home now a getaway for London money, Martin is displaced to the estate above the picturesque harbour. As his struggle to restore the family to their traditional place creates increasing friction with tourists and locals alike, a tragedy at the heart of the family changes his world.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4225,"vote_count":95,"poster_path":"/cr6T1ygg5jD3zyqmbR7l2TPaHkN.jpg","release_date":"2019-03-26","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/vXXeefOP1V1qwkPMzrwJ9taNto0.jpg","original_title":"Bait","original_language":"en"},{"id":1322218,"adult":false,"title":"Mononoke the Movie: Chapter II - The Ashes of Rage","video":false,"overview":"The Medicine Seller returns as the Edo harem faces a new crisis, with family feuds, inner turmoil and fiery envy igniting the birth of a raging spirit.","genre_ids":[16,14,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3216,"vote_count":24,"poster_path":"/tPExtAM958Gx07itJ7nWqSddBQ9.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-14","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/wDwfR4rDWRA2fLfLF14SdMOdHOZ.jpg","original_title":"劇場版モノノ怪 第二章 火鼠","original_language":"ja"},{"id":826796,"adult":false,"title":"Help","video":false,"overview":"Sarah seems to have found her calling working in a Liverpool care home where she has a special talent for connecting with the residents. Then, in March 2020, the Coronavirus pandemic hits.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7325,"vote_count":130,"poster_path":"/xuB589szYuTcBJ0lZa0MSGAf1Ok.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-16","vote_average":7.085,"backdrop_path":"/jRwqNjLsOiCzDJ4lT4dpFZemNx7.jpg","original_title":"Help","original_language":"en"},{"id":19935,"adult":false,"title":"Butterfly","video":false,"overview":"Flavia is a thirtysomething married teacher. She has suppressed the memory of her adolescent lesbian fling with Jin and is stuck in a stifling marriage. A chance encounter in a supermarket with the playful and seductive singer Yip reawakens dormant feelings and she begins to think back on her teenage affair with Jin.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7721,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/eIUa7LFUD660gKUKsohAXimtj1u.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-02","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/xPV38JBEnQCxLyM8iC0RmPCUJ13.jpg","original_title":"蝴蝶","original_language":"cn"},{"id":1249728,"adult":false,"title":"Magic Candies","video":false,"overview":"The other kids never ask Dong-Dong to play, but he’s fine just playing marbles on his own. Until one day, he buys a bag of colorful candies and begins to discover new voices and perspectives.","genre_ids":[16,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4088,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/3kaWCY3pUNG7lHmjL6GM8FtATrF.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-28","vote_average":6.786,"backdrop_path":"/2QQUXTZdHdh48K51aZKMlfaD6B1.jpg","original_title":"あめだま","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1355126,"adult":false,"title":"Sugar Mill","video":false,"overview":"A group of young men and women who work as seasonal workers in a sugar factory face terror from the kingdom of demons where the factory is located. They must find out the cause of the demons' anger, before the terror ends their lives.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.9628,"vote_count":24,"poster_path":"/z8Qy6WltFWdnMaQBowXrOr3Vfyg.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-31","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/3fNUHpIUVk4THb2CKScIZcdr1Kc.jpg","original_title":"Pabrik Gula","original_language":"id"}],"similar_content":[{"id":590252,"adult":false,"title":"The Gingerbread House","video":false,"overview":"Even children in an over-technified civilization need fairy tales, and Mrs. Fairy Tale invites them into her world. The woodcutter goes to the forest with his children, Hansel and Gretel. While their father works, the children pick strawberries. However, they get lost deep into the forest and lose their way back. After a sinister night, they find themselves in front of a honey gingerbread house. While peeling gingerbread, the witch catches them: she locks the skinny Hansel in a cage to fatten him up, and makes the plump Gretel her helper. However, benevolent angels watch over both children, appearing to them in their dreams and giving them hope for salvation.","genre_ids":[10751,14],"popularity":0.1786,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1933-12-22","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Perníková chaloupka","original_language":"cs"},{"id":763577,"adult":false,"title":"Spiritpact","video":false,"overview":"Yang Jinghua, a young heir to a family of exorcists, is left struggling alone after his parents’ deaths. Barely surviving, he encounters the wealthy and skilled exorcist Duanmu Xi while trying to fend off a spirit. After a fatal accident, Yang awakens to find himself in a contract with Duanmu Xi, marking the start of his new life.","genre_ids":[14],"popularity":0.2472,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/gQfa44P8piUHJ8A7bP6j0PXBNEy.jpg","release_date":"2018-03-11","vote_average":2.7,"backdrop_path":"/6P5Y2u2HrnOrTVQXTNDUNsJpSiS.jpg","original_title":"灵契","original_language":"zh"},{"id":671,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","video":false,"overview":"Harry Potter has lived under the stairs at his aunt and uncle's house his whole life. But on his 11th birthday, he learns he's a powerful wizard—with a place waiting for him at the Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. As he learns to harness his newfound powers with the help of the school's kindly headmaster, Harry uncovers the truth about his parents' deaths—and about the villain who's to blame.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":22.7137,"vote_count":29166,"poster_path":"/wuMc08IPKEatf9rnMNXvIDxqP4W.jpg","release_date":"2001-11-16","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/1XAC6RPT01UX9EQGy2JVn5c8pgy.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","original_language":"en"},{"id":672,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets","video":false,"overview":"Cars fly, trees fight back, and a mysterious house-elf comes to warn Harry Potter at the start of his second year at Hogwarts. Adventure and danger await when bloody writing on a wall announces: The Chamber Of Secrets Has Been Opened. To save Hogwarts will require all of Harry, Ron and Hermione's magical abilities and courage.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":16.148,"vote_count":23265,"poster_path":"/sdEOH0992YZ0QSxgXNIGLq1ToUi.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-13","vote_average":7.704,"backdrop_path":"/1stUIsjawROZxjiCMtqqXqgfZWC.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets","original_language":"en"},{"id":673,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","video":false,"overview":"Year three at Hogwarts means new fun and challenges as Harry learns the delicate art of approaching a Hippogriff, transforming shape-shifting Boggarts into hilarity and even turning back time. But the term also brings danger: soul-sucking Dementors hover over the school, an ally of the accursed He-Who-Cannot-Be-Named lurks within the castle walls, and fearsome wizard Sirius Black escapes Azkaban. And Harry will confront them all.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":15.6854,"vote_count":22845,"poster_path":"/aWxwnYoe8p2d2fcxOqtvAtJ72Rw.jpg","release_date":"2004-05-31","vote_average":8.009,"backdrop_path":"/vbk5CfaAHOjQPSAcYm6AoRRz2Af.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","original_language":"en"},{"id":674,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","video":false,"overview":"When Harry Potter's name emerges from the Goblet of Fire, he becomes a competitor in a grueling battle for glory among three wizarding schools—the Triwizard Tournament. But since Harry never submitted his name for the Tournament, who did? Now Harry must confront a deadly dragon, fierce water demons and an enchanted maze only to find himself in the cruel grasp of He Who Must Not Be Named.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":17.271,"vote_count":21865,"poster_path":"/fECBtHlr0RB3foNHDiCBXeg9Bv9.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-16","vote_average":7.801,"backdrop_path":"/8f9dnOtpArDrOMEylpSN9Sc6fuz.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","original_language":"en"},{"id":675,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","video":false,"overview":"Returning for his fifth year at Hogwarts, Harry is stunned to find that his warnings about the return of Lord Voldemort have been ignored. Left with no choice, Harry takes matters into his own hands, training a small group of motivated students to defend themselves against the Dark Arts.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":14.5713,"vote_count":20531,"poster_path":"/5aOyriWkPec0zUDxmHFP9qMmBaj.jpg","release_date":"2007-07-08","vote_average":7.672,"backdrop_path":"/pkxPkHOPJjOvzfQOclANEBT8OfK.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","original_language":"en"},{"id":767,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","video":false,"overview":"As Lord Voldemort tightens his grip on both the Muggle and wizarding worlds, Hogwarts is no longer a safe haven. Harry suspects perils may even lie within the castle, but Dumbledore is more intent upon preparing him for the final battle fast approaching. Together they work to find the key to unlock Voldemorts defenses and to this end, Dumbledore recruits his old friend and colleague Horace Slughorn, whom he believes holds crucial information. Even as the decisive showdown looms, romance blossoms for Harry, Ron, Hermione and their classmates. Love is in the air, but danger lies ahead and Hogwarts may never be the same again.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":13.7456,"vote_count":20501,"poster_path":"/z7uo9zmQdQwU5ZJHFpv2Upl30i1.jpg","release_date":"2009-07-15","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/ze6Mx4QE5mQVXRYmG2flncqqle4.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","original_language":"en"},{"id":2059,"adult":false,"title":"National Treasure","video":false,"overview":"Modern treasure hunters, led by archaeologist Ben Gates, search for a chest of riches rumored to have been stashed away by George Washington, Thomas Jefferson and Benjamin Franklin during the Revolutionary War. The chest's whereabouts may lie in secret clues embedded in the Constitution and the Declaration of Independence, and Gates is in a race to find the gold before his enemies do.","genre_ids":[12,28,53,9648],"popularity":5.7201,"vote_count":6727,"poster_path":"/pxL6E4GBOPUG6CdkO9cUQN5VMwI.jpg","release_date":"2004-11-19","vote_average":6.648,"backdrop_path":"/xXWT0je8dTFFNBq6P2CeTZkPUu2.jpg","original_title":"National Treasure","original_language":"en"},{"id":2062,"adult":false,"title":"Ratatouille","video":false,"overview":"Remy, a resident of Paris, possesses a palate far more refined than that of his fellow comrades. He dreams of becoming a chef, determined to create culinary masterpieces rather than scavenge for scraps. There’s just one small problem: Remy is a rat. When fate deposits him in the sewers beneath one of Paris’s most famous restaurants, he finds himself ideally placed to fulfill his dream. Forming an unusual alliance with a bumbling young kitchen worker, Remy begins a daring culinary double life. Together, they must outwit the scheming Head Chef Skinner, evade Remy’s disapproving colony, and impress renowned food critic Anton Ego, who strikes fear in the hearts of chefs all throughout France.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751,14],"popularity":13.5564,"vote_count":18193,"poster_path":"/t3vaWRPSf6WjDSamIkKDs1iQWna.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-28","vote_average":7.836,"backdrop_path":"/xgDj56UWyeWQcxQ44f5A3RTWuSs.jpg","original_title":"Ratatouille","original_language":"en"},{"id":949190,"adult":false,"title":"Berona","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[35,10751,14],"popularity":1.9266,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1967-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Berona","original_language":"sk"},{"id":953,"adult":false,"title":"Madagascar","video":false,"overview":"Four animal friends get a taste of the wild life when they break out of captivity at the Central Park Zoo and wash ashore on the island of Madagascar.","genre_ids":[10751,16,12,35],"popularity":8.9954,"vote_count":11528,"poster_path":"/zMpJY5CJKUufG9OTw0In4eAFqPX.jpg","release_date":"2005-05-25","vote_average":6.921,"backdrop_path":"/tPaurpIUskVji5vwV0dhy9pq4Vs.jpg","original_title":"Madagascar","original_language":"en"},{"id":2120,"adult":false,"title":"Cedric","video":false,"overview":"Death as a global service provider? Unthinkable! So far Death has thought that too. But then his nephew Cedric had the crazy idea of founding the company AFTER LIFE while his uncle was away. This company takes over the craft of death with the latest technology and markets it worldwide.","genre_ids":[16,10751],"popularity":0.1481,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/v158R46vHrjpKQqP1bwVni2RGxJ.jpg","release_date":"2006-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/m1CSCeQtLN5bHrclX8JtADzXBlH.jpg","original_title":"Cedric","original_language":"de"},{"id":808,"adult":false,"title":"Shrek","video":false,"overview":"It ain't easy bein' green -- especially if you're a likable (albeit smelly) ogre named Shrek. On a mission to retrieve a gorgeous princess from the clutches of a fire-breathing dragon, Shrek teams up with an unlikely compatriot -- a wisecracking donkey.","genre_ids":[16,35,14,12,10751],"popularity":21.571,"vote_count":18414,"poster_path":"/iB64vpL3dIObOtMZgX3RqdVdQDc.jpg","release_date":"2001-05-18","vote_average":7.757,"backdrop_path":"/sRvXNDItGlWCqtO3j6wks52FmbD.jpg","original_title":"Shrek","original_language":"en"},{"id":810,"adult":false,"title":"Shrek the Third","video":false,"overview":"The King of Far Far Away has died and Shrek and Fiona are to become King & Queen. However, Shrek wants to return to his cozy swamp and live in peace and quiet, so when he finds out there is another heir to the throne, they set off to bring him back to rule the kingdom.","genre_ids":[14,12,16,35,10751],"popularity":9.2125,"vote_count":9623,"poster_path":"/n4SexGGQzI26E269tfpa80MZaGV.jpg","release_date":"2007-05-17","vote_average":6.303,"backdrop_path":"/wvXxKpFGXvQJRB0nvvfURhRD3C0.jpg","original_title":"Shrek the Third","original_language":"en"},{"id":812,"adult":false,"title":"Aladdin","video":false,"overview":"In the boorish city of Agrabah, kind-hearted street urchin Aladdin and Princess Jasmine fall in love, although she can only marry a 